= {{non_q_project_name_short}} System Requirements =
== Minimum ==
* 1 GB free RAM - with Whonix-Gateway lowered to 256 MB. {{Minimum RAM}}
* 10 GB free hard drive space.

== Recommended ==
* Additional hard drive space when installing applications into the Whonix-Workstation.
* A CPU with [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X86_virtualization#AMD_virtualization_.28AMD-V.29 AMD-V] or Intel [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X86_virtualization#Intel_virtualization_.28VT-x.29 VT-x].

== For Best Performance ==
* A solid state drive (SSD).
* Additional RAM to dedicate to the {{workstation_product_name}} when multitasking.

== Notes ==
* {{workstation_product_name}} can be run with 256 MB RAM when not using a desktop environment. {{Minimum RAM}}
* For low memory and console-only configurations, see [[Desktop#RAM_Adjusted_Desktop_Starter|Ram Adjusted Desktop Starter]].
* Systems without AMD-V or Intel VT-x might experience the PAE or "{{Code2|VERR_SSM_FIELD_NOT_CONSECUTIVE}}" error; please read [[VirtualBox/Troubleshooting#PAE_crash|PAE Crash]] for a workaround.
* Linux users with low RAM might save some host RAM if a lighter desktop environment like Xfce or LXDE is configured, rather than KDE, GNOME and other alternatives.

